leaftop (0.2) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Added details to resource pages
  * Added more process grouping options (flat, tree, cgroup)
  * Added ability to set process priority/nice
  * Added disk and network usage to status bar
  * It is now possible to send all standard signals
  * Some UI tweaks
  * Improved startup performance
  * Fixed a random crash

